Chemi & Cotex Sells Stake to Private Funds, Reuters Reports

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-02-16T13:16:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/chemi-cotex-sells-stake-to-private-funds-reuters-reports.html
A group of private funds bought a
majority stake in  Tanzania ’s Chemi & Cotex Industries Ltd.,
 Reuters  said, citing Paul Kavuma, chief executive officer of the
Catalyst Fund.  The equity funds include Direct Principal Investments, a
division of HSBC Holdings Plc, Satya Capital and Catalyst
Principal Partners, the news agency reported.  Chemi & Cotex is a consumer goods business in East Africa’s
second largest economy, producing toothpaste, cosmetics and food
products, Reuters said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mkhululi Mancotywa in Johannesburg at 
 mmancotywa1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Amanda Jordan in  London  at 
 ajordan11@bloomberg.net . 